            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>+ In nomine domini Dei salvaturi nostri Iesum Christi. Regnante
                        domno nostro Liutprand viro exctelentissimo rege, anno regni eius octavo,
                        per indictione septima; feliciter. Ideo Deo auturem cunstat me <persName
                            key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Aunefridus de Guamo"
                            >Aunefrid</name></persName> vir venerabilis <rs key="#Other_clerics"
                            >clirico</rs> ac die repromisse et repromisi me servire ad beato
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/226">sancto Laurentio
                            et sancti Valentini</orgName> amturi meo cum homnia ris mea quod mihi
                        etvineret, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs>, <rs key="#Slave">servus vel ancilla</rs>, cultum, desertum,
                        movile vel inmovile sesseque moventivus; casa quod in
                            <placeName>Arno</placeName> avire visi sumus in loco qui dicitor
                            <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Wine #Slave"
                            ref="#places/579">Muniana</placeName>, sorte mea, uvicumque fueret, ad
                        beato sancto Laurentio et sancti Valentini sit quantum da germanis mei
                        evineret. Sic tamen, ut, dum die vite me fueret, in mea sit potestatem
                        usumfructu, et pos viro ovitum meum de ipsa sorticellula mea aveas potestas
                        vivendum <persName key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales"><name ref="Rotberga"
                                >Rotperga</name></persName> et <persName key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales"
                                ><name ref="Bertcunda">Perticunda</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Nuns/sanctimoniales">ancille Dei</rs>. Et si forsitans aliquis de
                        sororis aut nepotis Dominus advocare ad velamen ad ipso sancto loco, ut
                        aveas licentia ad vivendum de ipsa sorticella quod ipsi Aunifrid clirico
                        fice ad ipso sancto loco. Tamen sic aveamus licentia, si forsitans alequa
                        causa opus fueret pro causa sancti Laurenti aut sancti Valentini, ut
                        licentia aveas pro ipso sancto loco vindere; nam non pro alia causa. Actum
                        in <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/180">Vaccule</placeName> prope
                            <rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs> Sancti Laurenti et Sancti Valentini,
                        per mense martio, indictione et regnum suprascriptum; feliciter. Signum +
                        manus Aunifrid vir venerabilis clirico anc cartula fieri rogaui. Signum +
                        manus <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Balduinus"
                            >Paldoin</name></persName> vir venerabilis <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presviter</rs> cumsentientem Aunefrid advocandum. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gundualdus"
                            >Gudualdi</name></persName> testis. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Tachipertus">Tachipert</name></persName> filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Tappulus">Tappuli</name></persName>. Signum +
                        manus <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name
                                ref="Mangnualdus">Magnuald</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis. Signum + manus
                            <persName key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name
                                ref="Firmicianus">Firmiciani</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> testis. Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Other_clerics"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                            >Teutpert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clirico</rs> rogatus et petitus ad Aunefrid viro
                        venerabili clirico iscrivere cartula cunfermationis; et est avitator in
                            <placeName ref="#places/179">Guamo</placeName>. Ego <persName
                            key="#Copyist"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> scripsi in
                        hanc pagina renovationis quantum in autentico invenire potui, nec amplius
                        iuncxi, nec menime feci, sine dolo uel fraude excemplavi. </ab>
                        </div>
